# Club Project API Lookup

When the user asks about APIs, curl commands, requests, or "what happens in [screen name]" for any screen:

## 1. Source of Truth: Club Project (nahdi-mobile)

The **club project** is nahdi-mobile at:
```
/Users/eslamwaheedrafat/StudioProjects/nahdi-mobile
```

## 2. Where to Find API Info

- **Endpoints**: `lib/features/<feature>/data/endpoints/` or `*_endpoints.dart`
- **Datasources**: `lib/features/<feature>/data/datasource/` or `*_datasource_impl.dart` (shows how APIs are called)
- **Base URL**: `https://b12.nahdionline.com/` (main API) or `https://sso.nahdionline.com/` (auth)
- **Common headers**: `client_id`, `locale=en-SA`, `device=app`, `Accept`, `Content-Type`

## 3. Key Feature Paths (Club Project)

| Screen/Feature | Endpoints File |
|----------------|----------------|
| Splash | `lib/features/splash/data/endpoints/splash_url_endpoints.dart` |
| Mama Club | `lib/features/mama_club/data/mama_club_endpoints.dart` |
| Login/Auth | `lib/features/auth/presentation/data/auth_endpoints.dart` |
| Home | `lib/features/main/home/data/endpoints/home_endpoints.dart` |
| Cart | `lib/features/cart/data/cart_endpoints.dart` |
| Checkout | `lib/features/checkout/data/checkout_endpoints.dart` |
| Orders | `lib/features/order/data/order_endpoints.dart` |

## 4. Adding to the Dashboard

- **APIs with curl**: Add to `lib/data/api_data.dart` as `PageInfo` / `ApiInfo`
- **Screen docs**: Add to `lib/screens_documentation/data/screens_data.dart` as `ScreenInfoModel`
- **Curl format**: `curl -X METHOD "https://b12.nahdionline.com/ENDPOINT?locale=en-SA&device=app" -H "accept: application/json" -H "Content-Type: application/json" -H "client_id: dddc5530-fbc5-4a30-bf63-3d3d7f63de6b" -L -k`

## 5. Workflow

1. User asks: "What APIs does the splash screen call?" or "Get me the curl for Mama Club"
2. Search/look at nahdi-mobile at the relevant feature path
3. Extract endpoint, method, description from datasource/endpoints
4. Provide the info and optionally add it to `lib/data/api_data.dart`
